# Social Media Reports Directory

This directory contains weekly and monthly social media performance reports.

## Structure

```
reports/
├── weekly/
│   ├── 2026-W10.md
│   ├── 2026-W11.md
│   └── ...
└── monthly/
    ├── 2026-03.md
    ├── 2026-04.md
    └── ...
```

## Report Generation

Weekly reports are generated every Monday via GitHub Actions.
See `.github/workflows/social-report.yml` for automation.

## Manual Entry

Until platform API integration is complete, metrics should be entered manually
following the templates in `KPI_FRAMEWORK.md`.
